detaileddescription.para: Autodetect the best available SHA256 implementation. Returns the name of the implementation.

memberdef.argsstring: (unsigned char *out, const unsigned char *in, size_t blocks)
memberdef.name: SHA256D64

detaileddescription.para: Compute multiple double-SHA256's of 64-byte blobs. output: pointer to a blocks*32 byte output buffer input: pointer to a blocks*64 byte input buffer blocks: the number of hashes to compute.
